\h4(show_number=false){[rand.req.urng]}

Change \eelis{rand.req.urng#3} as follows:

\Bdiff{
A class \tcode{G} meets the \dfn{uniform random bit generator} requirements if
\ul{
  \li{
    \tcode{G} models \tcode{uniform_random_bit_generator},
  }
  \li{
    \tcode{invoke_result_t<G&>} is an unsigned integer type
    \ins{other than a bit-precise integer type}\iref{basic.fundamental}, and
  }
  \li{
    \tcode{G} provides a nested \grammarterm{typedef-name} \tcode{result_type}
    that denotes the same type as \tcode{invoke_result_t<G&>}.
  }
}
}

\editnote{
The addition of bullets is part of the change.
}

