\h4(show_number=false){[stream.types]}

Change \eelis{stream.types} as follows:

\Bdiff{
\itemdecl{
using streamoff = \exposid{implementation-defined};
}

\itemdescr{
The type \tcode{streamoff} is a synonym for
\del{one of the signed basic integral types}
\ins{a standard signed integer type}
of sufficient size to represent the maximum possible file size for the operating system.
}

\itemdecl{
using streamsize = \exposid{implementation-defined};
}

\itemdescr{
The type \tcode{streamsize} is a synonym for
\del{one of the signed basic integral types}
\ins{a standard signed integer type}.
It is used to represent the number of characters
transferred in an I/O operation, or the size of I/O buffers.
}
}

